parameters:
Captain Agua: Sorry, but I can't set sail. Please wait until
the issue is resolved for safety reasons.

Clea: I apologize for interrupting. I have come from the
Adventurer's Guild to help resolve the issue.

Clea: Of course, young explorer Ect, who is a member of the
